<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=673&amp;p=701#p701"><![CDATA[
11/20 (Sun.) 13 everyday habits that make you smarter / How the internet changing friendship (Host: Jennie)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------<br />Session I: 13 everyday habits that make you smarter<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/173315">https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/173315</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Please select the top 3 out of the 13 habits that you agree with and why?<br /><br />2. Please share us with what habits out of the13 that you have been working on?<br /><br />3. What kind of games do you play to make you think?  Please share us with your       valuable experiences.  <br /><br />4.The big one according to the video, hang out with people who are smarter than        you. How do you think about it? <br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session II: How the internet changing friendship<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/84576">https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/84576</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Are you an active person on social media?  How many platforms are you using now?<br /><br />2.Have you joined any other groups that you are interested in over social media?       Please share us with your experiences.<br /><br />3.Have you ever made new contacts or located those friends in the old days     because of the social media? Please share us with your experiences.<br />    <br />4.In your contacts on social media, some are dormants and some are    commemorative. Do you agree that friendship on social media is shallower?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Wed Nov 16, 2022 4:26 pm</p><hr />
